sentences: The production company (Aje Filmworks) has produced a number of videos, out of Kiss Daniel's 2016 New Era Album, videos which have been enjoying massive airplay and have to a large extent associated the Aje Filmworks brand with Kiss Daniel.

In October 2006 AJE filmworks was founded by Anietie James a prolific Nigerian video director & visual storyteller whose detailed and exceptional works have been recognised in the Nigerian, African mainstream entertainment and creative industry.
